tables.First: 1850 May 20 Prior to 1850, Surrey scorecards do not indicate who captained the side, but as club captain it was probably Charles Hoare.

tables.Name: Lord Dalmeny Harry Primrose, 6th Earl of Rosebery, was known as Lord Dalmeny at the time of his captaincy.

tables.Name: Mark Butcher In the absence through injury of Mark Butcher for most of the 2005 season, [[Mark Ramprakash]] led the side. In the absence through injury of Mark Butcher for most of the 2009 season, [[Stewart Walters]] led the side.
